description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacterium melaninogenicum; Bacteroides melaninogenicus; Bacteroides melaninogenicus melaninogenicus; Bacteroides melaninogenicus subsp. melaninogenicus; Fusiformis nigrescens; Hemophilus melaninogenicus; Ristella melaninogenica.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
